Compute fold changes given Contrasts 2

Source: R/tidyMS_application.R
workflow_missigness_impute_contrasts.Rd

Compute fold changes given Contrasts 2

workflow_missigness_impute_contrasts(
  data,
  config,
  contrasts,
  agg_fun = function(x) {     median(x, na.rm = TRUE) },
  global = TRUE
)

Examples

library(LFQService)
library(tidyverse)
bb <- LFQServiceData::skylinePRMSampleData_A
configur <- bb$config_f()
data <- bb$analysis(bb$data, configur)

#> creating sampleName
#> completing cases
configur$parameter$qVal_individual_threshold <- 0.01
data <- LFQService::removeLarge_Q_Values(data, configur)
data <- complete_cases(data, configur)

#> completing cases
unique(data$Time)

#> [1] "T8"   "T2"   "T24"  "T336" "T0"   "T240" "T72"  "T168"
Contrasts <- c("timeT24-T8" = "TimeT24-TimeT8", "timeT72-T8" = "TimeT72 - TimeT8")
res <- workflow_missigness_impute_contrasts(data, configur, Contrasts)

#> completing cases
#> missigness_impute_factors_interactions : imputed
#> timeT24-T8=TimeT24-TimeT8
#> timeT72-T8=TimeT72 - TimeT8
#> completing cases
#> missigness_impute_factors_interactions : meanArea
#> timeT24-T8=TimeT24-TimeT8
#> timeT72-T8=TimeT72 - TimeT8
res("long", "factors")
